<div class="hero-header">
    <div class="hero-image-container">
        <%= image_tag "hero-header-image.jpg", class: "hero-image" %>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-text-container">
        <h1>Anything Goes</h1>
        <h3>Need a job done? Find your perfect candidate today!</h3>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-home">
    <h1>A diverse job market place</h1>
    <div class="blurb-container flex space-around">
        <div class="blurb-home">
            <%= image_tag "icon-example.jpg", class: "blurb-image" %>
            <h2 class="blurb-heading">Choice</h2>
            <p>Anything Goes is full of candidates and jobs that you can access to get to work or find the right person for your own jobs. All you have to do is signup and provide your experience to get started and make an income!</p>
                <%= link_to "Learn more", class: "button-card" %>
        </div>
        <div class="blurb-home">
            <%= image_tag "icon-example.jpg", class: "blurb-image" %>
            <h2 class="blurb-heading">Community</h2>
            <p>Anything Goes is a new application, which means our user base is fresh with lots of room to get creative with your job postings or applications. No crazy algorithms to suppress your profile, everyone has a fair chance!</p>
                <%= link_to "Learn more", class: "button-card" %>
        </div>
        <div class="blurb-home">
            <%= image_tag "icon-example.jpg", class: "blurb-image" %>
            <h2 class="blurb-heading">Growing</h2>
            <p>Anything Goes is a growing community of people who are seeking to work and find workers not matter the job. Since our start, Anything Goes has already built up its own community of hard workers all around the world.</p>
                <%= link_to "Learn more", class: "button-card" %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-home grey">
    <h1>Jobs and Candidates in your area</h1>
