        <div class="card-home">
            <%= image_tag "icon-example.jpg", class: "card-image" %>
            <div class="padding">
                <h2 class="blurb-heading">Global</h2>
                <p>We give our users the reach to be able to work and find canidates anywhere in the world. Provided you can do the work, it doesn't matter who you or where you work.</p>
                    <%= link_to "Learn more", class: "button-card" %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-home">
            <%= image_tag "icon-example.jpg", class: "card-image" %>
            <div class="padding">
                <h2 class="blurb-heading">Control</h2>
                <p>Whether you are deciding on which job to take or how to price your posted job, everything is totally in your control with no fear of being thrown into Anything Goes Prison.</p>
                    <%= link_to "Learn more", class: "button-card" %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-home">
            <%= image_tag "icon-example.jpg", class: "card-image" %>
            <div class="padding">
                <h2 class="blurb-heading">Easy</h2>
                <p>Anything Goes is an easy to use, no frills platform. All you need to do is sign up, post a job, apply for a job and accept or decline jobs. The rest is up to you!</p>
                    <%= link_to "Learn more", class: "button-card" %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

